ncaa_bb_player_box_score

Source: R/ncaa_bb_player_box_score.R
ncaa_bb_player_box_score.Rd

Obtains basketball game player box scores from the NCAA API.

ncaa_bb_player_box_score(game_id)

Arguments

game_id

the game_id of a given NCAA BB game from the NCAA API

Value

a data frame with NCAA BB player box score data for the given game

Examples

# \donttest{
  ncaa_bb_player_box_score(5897924)
